CAR - Cyber Analytics Repository
-developed based on MITRE ATT&CK adversary model
-validated and well-explained analytics

eg. Scheduled Task  - File Access
-pseudocode provided by CAR

EQL - Event Query Language https://eql.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
-utilized to query, parse and organize Sysmon event data

https://github.com/mitre-attack/bzar - Bro/Zeek

